## TS2532: Object is possibly 'undefined'

**Symptoms:**
- `Object is possibly 'undefined'`
- `Object is possibly 'null'`
- Strict null checks catching potential errors

**Solutions:**

```typescript
// Method 1: Non-null assertion (if you're sure)
function process(user?: User) {
  console.log(user!.name);  // Asserts user exists
}

// Method 2: Optional chaining (safer)
function process(user?: User) {
  console.log(user?.name);  // undefined if user is undefined
}

// Method 3: Nullish coalescing (with default)
