```
□ Use backdrop-filter for glass effects
□ Add subtle border (1px, low opacity white)
□ Include inset highlight for top edge
□ Animate with cubic-bezier, not linear
□ Test on dark AND light backgrounds
□ Ensure text contrast meets WCAG AA (4.5:1)
□ Add fallback for browsers without backdrop-filter
□ Keep blur values reasonable (10-40px)
□ Use transform: translateZ(0) for GPU acceleration
```

