## 🎨 Color Trends 2026

**Pantone Color of 2026: Cloud Dancer** — soft, calm, breathable

### The Shift
- Moving AWAY from bold, saturated "grab attention" colors
- Moving TOWARD softer palettes that reduce visual fatigue
- Pair quiet neutrals with warm accent tones for depth

### Practical Tips
```css
/* 2026 Calm Palette */
:root {
  --bg-soft: #f8f9fa;
  --text-primary: #1f2937;
  --accent-warm: #C4A052;  /* Your existing gold — on trend! */
  --accent-calm: #2563eb;
}
```

