## 🔤 Typography Trends

### Kinetic Typography
Text that moves, morphs, responds.

```css
.kinetic-title {
  animation: textGlow 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes textGlow {
  from { text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.5); }
  to { text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.8); }
}
```

### Variable Fonts
One font file, infinite weights/widths.

```css
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Inter';
  src: url('Inter-Variable.woff2') format('woff2');
  font-weight: 100 900;
}

.heading { font-variation-settings: 'wght' 700; }
.body { font-variation-settings: 'wght' 400; }
